title: MilkShake
text:
MilkShake is a Thai pop girl group that formed under the HALO Society label in affiliation with GMM Grammy agency in 2015 in Bangkok, Thailand.


== Members ==
Warunthorn Thiemsak (Bam Bam)
Phattrapreya Younyao (Taton)
Pornnappan Pornpenpipat (NeNe)
KwanJai Chaichankul
Prapatsorn Thitiprechar (Ginnii)
